chat.msg: First, walk a few steps to the left, passing under a wooden bench, then cross the path
now do a u-turn to the left, cross the trail again, and go back towards where we started with the white dog
cool. now walk beyond the bench heading south
Busque otro perro blanco cerca de un picnic. dirígete en esa dirección
after the picnic, keep heading west, but brush by a bowl of berries
alrighty, keep this vibe! go north, over the wooden branch, across the river
don't go straight into the bush! circle it from the right until you see a florist stand
hah, well, keep going west, pass the florist stand, and head towards a big bridge with bikers on it
alright, keep moving, see the elderly folks on the bench? pass them and get yourself between them and a wooden branch
next, go a couple steps south
Deberías ver una rama de madera y un arbusto verde. ve entre ellos hacia el este
let me know once you see a young brown deer, should be just a few steps
¡impresionante! ¡Navegaste por ese camino como un campeón!
ha sido un placer ayudarte! pasemos a otra aventura cuando quieras
de nada, amigo! nos vemos la próxima vez
well done! you've made it to the end
alto! you made it to the deer

chat.msg: hola, q tal? ready to go?
cool! let's start with the palm trees
camina justo debajo del primero en dirección suroeste
sigue hasta que pases el segundo árbol, luego gira a la izquierda antes del tercero
alright! spot that brown puppy? let's move to its left, make a slight left and then a right heading south
perfect. see those rocks? go between them
Uno grande a tu izquierda, uno pequeño a tu derecha. ¡chocarás en el agua! no te preocupes, nos vamos a dar un chapuzón
look at that big red crab. head towards it, then turn right (west) following the large rock
súper. see that medium rock? continue along it until you see a shark
Sí, escuchaste bien. un tiburón. ¡Gira bruscamente a la derecha cuando lo hagas!
cool! let's head back to dry land
sneak between that medium rock and the colorful ball. move north man!
now, veer a bit to the left and keep heading north-west
¡Esté atento a la carpa roja y al altavoz!
genial! now, make a move around the tent in an arc
then, let's head south towards the sea but stop before you get wet!
right at the shore, turn west and pass below that red kayak
great! take a right, go north alongside the kayak
now, look for a small green bush
